The web app have 3 Signature Featured to share.

1. You can see 12 option to donate with 4 category.You can see the details about the organization by clicking the card . and You can donate money on a fixed amount by a button .


2. In the donation page you can see the organization you have donated with short info like price,category,name. By default you will see 4 card even though you donated more than 4 org. There will a Show all button to show the all organization.

3. In this web app you can see statistics page where you can your donation ratio compare to 12 option to donated. 

4. ALL the pages are in single web application. That's mean if you route all page it not going to reload with is kind of annoying.